sentence.text: In humans, mutations in several genes involved in the Notch pathway are associated with SDV, with both autosomal recessive (regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II, skeletal system development, LFNG, HES7) and autosomal dominant (negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II) inheritance.
